(84, 'Barcelona & Ibiza 2026', 'barcelona-ibiza-2026-2', NULL, 'Barcelona & Ibiza 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel travel package centered around Barcelona & Ibiza, Spain. Highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg, ✅ 4-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation in Barcelona, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation in Ibiza. Travel window: May/June/July/August /September|October.', 'Barcelona & Ibiza 2026 is a curated NBGS Travel package for Barcelona & Ibiza, Spain. Pricing is per person sharing. Travel details: May/June/July/August /September|October. Package highlights include ✅ Return flights from Johannesburg, ✅ 4-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation in Barcelona, ✅ 3-Nights Accommodation in 4* Accommodation in Ibiza, ✅ Daily breakfast, ✅ Return airport & domestic transfers. A non-refundable deposit is required to confirm your booking. Full payment must be made before your selected travel dates. Accommodation is based on shared rooms, with single supplement rates available. Travel insurance is not included in the package and should be purchased separately. Meals and drinks not specifically mentioned are excluded. Optional activities such as club tickets and other experiences are not included in the package price. Visa assistance for the Schengen visa is provided. Personal items and expenses are the responsibility of the traveler.', 'Europe', 'Spain', 'Catalonia', 'Barcelona & Ibiza', 'Barcelona & Ibiza', 'package', 'Travel Package', '7 Nights / 8 Days', '42000.00', 'ZAR', 'per_person_sharing', 'From', '5000.00', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 'published', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[object Object]', 'Mon Apr 13 2026 02:26:19 GMT+0200 (South Africa Standard Time)', 'Mon Apr 13 2026 02:26:19 GMT+0200 (South Africa Standard Time)'),
